entries.journal_entry_description: Do whatever Jorgellansel of the Darkwalkers asks of you.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Jorgellansel wants you to defeat Skaak Tipper freejacks as part of your assault on their base.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Jorgellansel wants you to defeat Skaak Tipper vanguards as part of your assault on them.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Jorgellansel wants you to sow some chaos among the Skaak Tippers by assaulting their base. To achieve that, defeat some Skaak Tipper vanguards and some Skaak Tipper freejacks.
entries.task04_comm_message_text: I can see why Hugo sent you to me. You did well against those bestial Skaak Tippers. Continue by corrupting their database systems.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Jorgellansel wants you to sabotage some Skaak Tipper database systems.
entries.task06_comm_message_text: Good. Now one last thing, I think. Get me some weapon research notes from their researchers. I want to see what new toys the Skaak Tippers are developing.
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Jorgellansel wants you to get some weapon research notes from Skaak Tipper researchers.
entries.task07_journal_entry_title: Defeat Skaak Tipper Researchers and Collect Weapon Research Notes.
entries.task08_journal_entry_description: Return to Jorgellansel with the research notes.
